des: Anthony Servideo grounds out, second baseman Hunter Haas to pitcher Alfredo Zarraga.
Billy Cook singles on a ground ball to left fielder Richie Palacios.   Shayne Fontana to 2nd.
Frederick Bencosme pops out to catcher Nick Meyer in foul territory.
Alejo Lopez flies out to center fielder Richie Palacios.
Luis Liberato flies out to right fielder Niko Hulsizer.

Dawson Dimon grounds into a force out, third baseman Curtis Mead to second baseman Ronny Simon.   Geraldo Quintero out at 2nd.  Dawson Dimon advances to 2nd, on a throwing error by second baseman Ronny Simon.
